        "client_msg_id": "da178db4-11c2-476f-a402-e23e3acd3cf3",
        "text": "FREST was an acronym, but now it’s just a name. So it should probably be Frest?\n\nThere are exceptions, but the vast majority of let’s say networked software of any complexity is based on SQL.",
