        "client_msg_id": "ee05cbcf-ddf2-4329-8781-2f83514da654",
        "text": "I've only skimmed your post (I should be dayjobbing :sweat_smile:) but it sounds like there's a lot of overlap between your interests and the semantic web \/ rfds \/ sparql community?",
        "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
        "user_profile": {
            "avatar_hash": "07fbb70c0e39",
